# Copy to arrival_board.env and edit values:
#   cp -n arrival_board.env.example arrival_board.env

MTA_KEY=Insert MTA key here
STOP_ID=501627
POLL_SECONDS=10

# Font
FONT_PATH=/usr/share/fonts/truetype/dejavu/DejaVuSans.ttf

# Weather is tied to the stop when possible (so different stops can show different weather).
# Priority: STOP_LAT/STOP_LON (this stop's coords) -> geocode of stop name -> WEATHER_LAT/LON fallback.
# STOP_LAT / STOP_LON = this stop's location (use when you change STOP_ID so weather follows the stop).
# WEATHER_GEOCODE_SUFFIX = appended to stop name for geocoding (default ", New York City").
# WEATHER_LAT / WEATHER_LON = fallback when stop location is unknown (e.g. no geocode, no STOP_LAT/LON).
STOP_LAT=40.740
STOP_LON=-73.756
# WEATHER_LAT=40.740
# WEATHER_LON=-73.756
# WEATHER_GEOCODE_SUFFIX=, New York City

# Optional: background music and flip sound.
# Kiosk: leave APLAY_DEVICE unset so the kiosk's Pulse/PipeWire owns HDMI; the app sends audio to the server and does not need device access.
# With APLAY_DEVICE unset: PipeWire or PulseAudio is used via paplay; music and flip mix. No extra build flags.
# Only set APLAY_DEVICE=hdmi:... if you run as the user that owns the device (direct ALSA; flip pauses music).
# MUSIC_FILE=... SOUND_FLIP=... Second track (ferry): SI Ferry.wav in tools/. Music loops continuously (never stops).
# Each loop = play music at normal speed + gap until total = MUSIC_DURATION_SEC. Ferry plays over music every 5th loop.
# MUSIC_DURATION_SEC=23   (total cycle 23s; gap = 23 - actual file length)
# MUSIC_FILE_SEC=21       (actual file length in seconds; set if WAV header is wrong)
# Troubleshooting: AUDIO_DEBUG=1 logs paths and flip triggers to stderr; with ALSA, aplay/sox errors are shown.

# Optional: GTFS static for scheduled tiles (Express routes at stop 501627 need MTABC feed)
# Default: MTABC (MTA Bus Company) for QM8, QM5, QM35, etc. at Springfield Blvd/73 Av
# GTFS_BUS_URL=https://rrgtfsfeeds.s3.amazonaws.com/gtfs_busco.zip
# GTFS_CACHE_PATH=$HOME/arrival_board/gtfs_bus_cache.zip
# Queens-only feed (no QM8 at 501627): https://rrgtfsfeeds.s3.amazonaws.com/gtfs_q.zip
